      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v11.json",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 455,
      "message": "Hello Jimmy, to avoid this edge I am trying to create an edge between esr-vnfm and esr-system-info but I am not able to create the relationship. I've sent the details in mail.\n\nKindle let me know for it.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 879,
