      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 306,
      "message": "According to the discussion result with Multicloud team. There will not be a vim-name when register a VIM. The cloud-owner and cloud-region-id will be a readable message, so they use the two item to indicate a VIM. Anyway, ESR portal does not provide a box for users to input the vim-name either register a VIM or VNFM.",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 313,
        "name": "Li Zi",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "li.zi30@zte.com.cn",
        "username": "nancylizi"
      },
      "updated": "2017-10-11 07:56:17.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
    },
